Compile/run:
     - Compile using
            make MetroSim
     - run executable with
            ./MetroSim stationsFile passFile [commands]

Program Purpose:

This homework assignment handles a running train to accomodate passengers 
arriving at a station, riding the metro, and departing at their destination
station. The purpose was to design and create an implementation to modularize
code and work with documented libraries. To accomplish this, this program uses
vectors of structs and queues.

